{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"DERISK (E4, local Docker on arm64): official gerritcodereview/gerrit:3.14.1 boots cleanly on arm64 and serves REST (version '3.14.1'). Bare minor tags (3.14/3.13) DO NOT exist on Docker Hub — pin a patch tag (3.14.1/3.13.7/3.12.8; all publish arm64). The %2F-safe nginx reverse-proxy (proxy_pass with NO path, + an /mcp/ route for the MCP) passes 'nginx -t'. Operational note: keep a clear host-port plan (a co-tenant Keycloak on 8080 blocked an initial bind — trivial, but pin ports)."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782686371178712001,"uuid":"b8f52f07-8091-4bfd-9134-9e9761e6bd35"}